request.description:
Operator-only — returns all ExternalCreditBalance rows on this agent plus summary totals (count, credits, totalPurchased, totalSpent, totalRefunded). Sorted by lastPurchase desc.

Response:
```
{
  success: true,
  summary: { count, credits, totalPurchased, totalSpent, totalRefunded },
  wallets: [
    {
      wallet, credits, totalPurchased, totalSpent, totalRefunded,
      lastPurchase, lastUsed, createdAt
    }, ...
  ]
}
```

The gateway uses this fan-out from /admin/api/agent-wallets to render the 'Per-agent wallets' section on the admin /admin/wallets page. Available from v2.25.35.

Operator-only — returns recent ExternalPayment rows sorted by createdAt desc.

Response:
```
{
  success: true,
  payments: [
    {
      txHash, chain, serviceId, callerAgentId,
      amount, currency, creditsIssued, usdValue, createdAt
    }, ...
  ]
}
```

Notes: For credit-purchase records (serviceId === 'credit-purchase') the wallet identity is in callerAgentId (existing field — kept for backwards compatibility); currency / creditsIssued / usdValue are populated from v2.25.35 onwards. Pre-v2.25.35 records will show those three as null.

